name: Chia IOU
public_notice: Note that exchanges trading these tokens are trading Chia IOU tokens. For mainnet Chia tokens, refer to https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/chia

description.en: Please note, Chia is still in the pre-minting phase, where tokens are not transferable. The tokens in circulation are pre-deposit from miners, backed by their respective mining pools. When Chia mainnet tokens are live, these IOU tokens will be swapped for the mainnet tokens. The current Chia supply is 21410,000 tokens, among which 21000,000 are in control of the Chia team, 410 000 minted already. The amount of circulating tokens is small at first, and will reach 5 million or above in a year, which represents a high inflation rate. Gate.io lists the Chia token when it is still an IOU. The price might be hyped due to the small supply. When the mainnet tokens start to circulate sometime between May 3-4, more tokens will be deposited to exchanges, which might cause dramatic price fluctuation. Meanwhile, as more tokens minted, the high inflation rate will also pose great downside pressure to the market price. Please beware of the high risks and don’t just ape in. It is possible that the price might fluctuate dramatically or even plummet in a few days. We discourage non-professional traders from participating in trading.
